sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>HTTPRoute
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OIDC as OIDC Issuer<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/h2c
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Authenticated Request via Bearer Token

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/8443<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    Gateway->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>Forward request
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>TLS 1.2+ | ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview result<br/>(user identity, groups)
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>TLS 1.2+ | ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview result<br/>(allowed: true/false)

    alt Authorized
        Proxy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/h2c | Optional mTLS
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: Response
    else Denied
        Proxy-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over Prom,Upstream: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping (Hardcoded Allow)

    Prom->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 | Bearer Token (prometheus-k8s SA)
    Note right of Proxy: Hardcoded authorizer detects<br/>system:serviceaccount:openshift-monitoring:prometheus-k8s<br/>Auto-allows GET /metrics<br/>(no API server call needed)
    Proxy->>Upstream: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (localhost)
    Upstream-->>Proxy: Metrics response
    Proxy-->>Prom: Metrics response

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 3: OIDC JWT Authentication

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/8443<br/>Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
    Gateway->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>Forward request
    Proxy->>OIDC: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>Proxy: OIDC discovery document
    Proxy->>OIDC: GET /jwks<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>Proxy: JSON Web Key Set
    Note right of Proxy: Validate JWT signature,<br/>extract user/groups from claims
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST SubjectAccessReview<br/>TLS 1.2+ | ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorization result
    alt Authorized
        Proxy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS | Auth headers
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: Response
    else Denied
        Proxy-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end
